Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.53,0:01:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to lose anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.30,0:01:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.27,0:01:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.64,0:01:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You slacker!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.31,0:01:51.38,Sign,,0,0,0,,DO YOUR BEST\NOTANI
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.21,0:01:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.72,0:02:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I'm just... no good without you, Koizumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.37,0:02:12.54,Title,,0,0,0,,The Best Birthday in History
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.38,0:02:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just no good without you, Koizumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.75,0:02:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.32,0:02:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, summer vacation starts tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.05,0:02:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.22,0:02:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.56,0:02:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Koizumi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.86,0:02:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do over summer vacation?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.70,0:02:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What a nice dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.50,0:02:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Summer. The last summer of my high school life.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.44,0:02:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I still don't know how Otani feels, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.78,0:02:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna have some fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.65,0:02:58.62,Superscript,,0,0,0,,SUMMER SCHOOL SIGN UP
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.32,0:03:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You've forgotten you'll be taking entrance exams soon, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.49,0:03:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I completely forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.36,0:03:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,For the little idiots I just named,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.26,0:03:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,...the summer study session is compulsory.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.03,0:03:15.10,Superscript,,0,0,0,,Little Idiot
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.19,0:03:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to work hard to make up for your past laziness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.23,0:03:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.27,0:03:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You exam students don't get a summer vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.24,0:03:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.70,0:03:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,My precious summer...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.51,0:03:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,So in the end,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.45,0:03:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,...Chiharu-chan and Suzuki-kun are the only ones who don't have summer school.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.12,0:03:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because they have study dates at the library every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.46,0:03:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not dates. We just study.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.63,0:03:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But we'll be attending summer classes, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.89,0:03:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And here I thought I'd have the chance to have loads of fun...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.43,0:03:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, loads of fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.17,0:03:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,An idiot like you who misses all the important stuff,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.27,0:03:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,...sleeping away and not hearing the best part!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.00,0:03:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What's got you so angry these days?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.61,0:03:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So we've got to attend summer school again this year?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.94,0:04:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And here I thought I could have fun, now that I'm done with the basketball club.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.21,0:04:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I though you resigned so that you could concentrate on your studies?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.79,0:04:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.95,0:04:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.49,0:04:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,...at least I don't need an excuse to hang out with Otani over the summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.46,0:04:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it's not so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.96,0:04:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobu-chan, why didn't you plan study dates with Nakao-chi too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.33,0:04:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see why the one with red crosses all over her work should be asking me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.17,0:04:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.84,0:04:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you melting?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.85,0:04:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't take it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.45,0:04:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Want to go somewhere cool?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.28,0:04:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.99,0:04:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay! Paradise!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.16,0:04:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm revived!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.96,0:04:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What would you like to order?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.16,0:04:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes, yes. My order...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.23,0:04:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.73,0:04:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! A new item on the menu?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.63,0:04:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.00,0:04:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,One Polynesian Dancer!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.47,0:05:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you copying me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.81,0:05:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one who's copying me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.48,0:05:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go with the drink bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.98,0:05:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.21,0:05:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Same here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.15,0:05:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.05,0:05:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. Please wait one moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.86,0:05:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Chiharu-chan, that's a cute ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.56,0:05:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.73,0:05:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,When did you get that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.36,0:05:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Did Suzuki-kun give it to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.53,0:05:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It was your birthday not long ago, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.80,0:05:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah. Well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.54,0:05:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done, Suzuki-chi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.21,0:05:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.68,0:05:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Nobu-chan, you got something for your birthday too, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.65,0:05:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. A handbag!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.88,0:05:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry it was only a cheap one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.52,0:05:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.32,0:05:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It was given with love, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.92,0:05:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you Nobu-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.39,0:05:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too! I love love love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.69,0:05:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I love love love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.26,0:05:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's happy, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.73,0:05:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! That reminds me, it's almost Risa's birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.50,0:06:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Smirk... Smirk... Smirk...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.61,0:06:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What's with this atmosphere?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.08,0:06:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani-chi, naturally you'll be giving Koizumi-san a present, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.41,0:06:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.42,0:06:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, he just can't live without Koizumi-san, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.99,0:06:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.49,0:06:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that, anyway? A proposal?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.79,0:06:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What the hell?!\NYou guys were listening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.46,0:06:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We heard it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.89,0:06:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.56,0:06:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't say I couldn't live without her!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.70,0:06:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.73,0:06:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! It's none of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.63,0:06:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What's going on?!\NThis is getting on my nerves!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.04,0:06:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! Just be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.47,0:06:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,For the customer who ordered the Polynesian Dancer...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.61,0:06:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's here! My Polynesian Dancer!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.18,0:06:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Mmm... Polynesia...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.45,0:06:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.86,0:06:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.94,0:07:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Koizumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.64,0:07:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.35,0:07:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez! I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.85,0:07:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.52,0:07:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want for your birthday?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.73,0:07:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.29,0:07:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you refusing my good intentions?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.50,0:07:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly, what were you talking about yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.96,0:07:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That was... Just forget about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.17,0:07:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.67,0:07:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No one is telling me anything, and everyone seems to find it hilarious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.94,0:07:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really irritating me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.97,0:07:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget it, okay. Just tell me what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.21,0:07:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing. I don't want anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.64,0:07:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.64,0:07:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't complain to me later if I don't give you anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.85,0:07:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you I don't want anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.99,0:08:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you always make things worse?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.19,0:08:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I just unconsciously—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.40,0:08:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.10,0:08:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.90,0:08:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.50,0:08:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want a cute ring or a handbag.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.24,0:08:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The only thing I want is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.71,0:08:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,...Otani's love!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.58,0:08:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Get away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.85,0:08:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.69,0:08:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeesh. It's so hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.76,0:08:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh. What a nice breeze.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.13,0:08:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,My birthday, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.50,0:08:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, on my birthday last year...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.11,0:08:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I like you, Otani!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.38,0:09:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with you? Saying a thing like that out of nowhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.05,0:09:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You're embarrassing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.92,0:09:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I wasn't taken seriously, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.22,0:09:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a whole year since then, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.26,0:09:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Umibouzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.60,0:09:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe someone like you is more suited to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.51,0:09:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.88,0:09:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Just talking to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.35,0:09:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a real idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.09,0:09:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Accept it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.06,0:09:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Ko-Koizumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.60,0:09:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Koizumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.24,0:10:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.81,0:10:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had enough of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.81,0:10:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm through with loving you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.55,0:10:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot's happened, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.21,0:10:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if my hard work has paid off?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.52,0:10:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, he just can't live without Koizumi-san, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.19,0:10:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I never said I can't live without her!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.49,0:10:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What were they talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.33,0:10:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're going to buy something, hurry up and do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.74,0:10:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We're kind of out of place here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.40,0:10:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I think she'll be happy with anything you get her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.98,0:10:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not doing it. I'm not buying anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.88,0:10:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,This is stupid. It feels wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.31,0:10:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You're not?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.98,0:10:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't give her Umibouzu stuff again. That's boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.52,0:10:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Why should your boredom be my concern?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.36,0:11:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope something good happens on my birthday this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.01,0:11:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Risa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.01,0:11:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.41,0:11:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to attend summer classes too, Haruka?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.41,0:11:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope. I just wanted to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.88,0:11:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruka-senpai may not look very smart,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.92,0:11:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,...but he's quick to understand things, so he does well on tests.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.85,0:11:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Seiko-chin...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.39,0:11:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, Koizumi-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.36,0:11:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.86,0:11:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,An invitation to Koizumi Risa's Birthday Party?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.20,0:11:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. We're going to prepare lots of delicious food and cake and host it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.87,0:11:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Invite everyone, okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.04,0:11:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You guys are so nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.28,0:11:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I am, huh. Feel free to fall for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.18,0:11:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Not gonna happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.05,0:11:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,How cruel!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.25,0:11:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget it. I'll just win you over with my party hosting skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.49,0:11:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.22,0:12:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Here. Take one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.56,0:12:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.63,0:12:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,An invitation to Koizumi-senpai's birthday party.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.96,0:12:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Please come, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.23,0:12:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,For Koizumi's birthday?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.50,0:12:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm inviting you because I don't have a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.13,0:12:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Better this than having you two off alone somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.97,0:12:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruka-senpai! Did you really have such an underhanded motive?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.08,0:12:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Say what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.58,0:12:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to let you have Risa all to yourself on her birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.98,0:12:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the worst!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.11,0:12:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I want to celebrate with her too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.99,0:12:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Nakao and Nobu-chan are both planning to go to your party, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.82,0:12:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Maity-sensei is going to come too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.13,0:12:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you, Otani?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.70,0:12:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to come?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.13,0:12:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you didn't want me to do anything for your birthday?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.43,0:12:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You said you didn't want a present from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.34,0:12:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I didn't mean it like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.84,0:12:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what did you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.08,0:12:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what does "can't live without me" mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.95,0:12:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I said I didn't say that!\NAs if I'd say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.92,0:13:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.35,0:13:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Did this happen when I fell asleep that time?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.99,0:13:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I told you, they got it all wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.16,0:13:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Man. I'm seriously going to get those guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.02,0:13:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what about the party?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.66,0:13:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I care!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.73,0:13:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Otani!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.17,0:13:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.57,0:13:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry I'm late!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.34,0:13:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy birthday to you,\N happy birthday to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.82,0:13:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,...happy birthday dear Risa...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.39,0:13:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,...happy birthday to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.23,0:13:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations, Risa!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.77,0:13:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.14,0:13:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure had a long talk with our homeroom teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.67,0:13:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What did he call you for?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.71,0:13:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, my test results were pretty terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.08,0:14:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Where's Otani-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.02,0:14:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.35,0:14:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.05,0:14:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We thought he was with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.42,0:14:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what about the party?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.66,0:14:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I care!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.53,0:14:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, maybe he went home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.90,0:14:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares if he's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.77,0:14:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Risa.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.04,0:14:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruka-senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.70,0:14:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,...don't tell me this is your doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.81,0:14:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't do a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.17,0:14:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! This aggressive reaction is very suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.68,0:14:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.91,0:14:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh! He's getting worse!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.08,0:14:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop this nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.55,0:14:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, now. Let's put that aside.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.82,0:14:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,"Put that aside"?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.62,0:14:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy birthday, Koizumi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.29,0:14:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Maity-sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.39,0:14:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.63,0:14:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.13,0:14:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, take a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.87,0:14:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the guest of honor today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.47,0:15:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! I put all of my love for you into this food, just to make you happy, Risa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.07,0:15:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! It smells so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.38,0:15:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.58,0:15:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait Risa. What about Otani-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.71,0:15:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! This cake is super cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.52,0:15:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it? I decorated it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.52,0:15:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind that. Check this out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.09,0:15:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I made all your favorites: chirashizushi, fried chicken, sandwiches, takoyaki, french fries,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.29,0:15:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,...and spaghetti with Neapolitan sauce!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.20,0:15:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.57,0:15:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not answering his phone.\NWhere could Otani have gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.84,0:15:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on! This is so frustrating!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.21,0:15:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,They're definitely both interested in each other now...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.71,0:15:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.98,0:15:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.98,0:15:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if Otani isn't around, everyone else is here celebrating with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.29,0:15:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh. That was just delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.56,0:15:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You're very welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.66,0:16:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, did you hear something from outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.23,0:16:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. It's probably fireworks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.40,0:16:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah. I heard there's a fireworks festival today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.83,0:16:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.20,0:16:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,If we go up to the roof, we should be able to see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.04,0:16:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Fireworks?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.21,0:16:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, last year too...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.14,0:16:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Risa, let's go up to the roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.48,0:16:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! I can see them! I can see them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.15,0:16:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,How pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.49,0:16:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Beautiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.06,0:16:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.16,0:16:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.21,0:16:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought watching the fireworks would cheer you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.88,0:16:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow. They sure are pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.52,0:16:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It really is no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.69,0:17:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If Otani's not with me, I just don't find the fireworks pretty...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.56,0:17:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,...and I can't cheer up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.10,0:17:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yo, this is for real. You got mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.90,0:17:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yo, this is for real. You got mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.00,0:17:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Mail?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.57,0:17:19.81,Superscript,,0,0,0,,Otani
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.57,0:17:19.81,Superscript,,0,0,150,,Behind you
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.10,0:17:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.10,0:17:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Something you didn't want.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.51,0:17:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,A present.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.78,0:17:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.94,0:17:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would I lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.54,0:17:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I open it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.65,0:17:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already opened it, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.31,0:17:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not my style,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.62,0:18:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,...but you always have rabbit stuff, so I just went and...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.39,0:18:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! It's super cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.19,0:18:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep it down! They'll see us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.93,0:18:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.59,0:18:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.83,0:18:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Fireworks. I bought them at the convenience store.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.13,0:18:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Cool. Then let's get everyone and—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.33,0:18:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do that later.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.60,0:18:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Just put that away for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.30,0:18:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,This?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.78,0:18:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,If they find out I bought you that,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.15,0:18:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,...they won't let me live it down, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.19,0:18:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you were late because you went to buy this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.76,0:18:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did you go to get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.06,0:18:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it matter where?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.64,0:18:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks. I'm really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.64,0:18:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.71,0:19:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you weren't going to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.32,0:19:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just thinking, "I guess I'm just no good without Otani."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.10,0:19:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.47,0:19:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.94,0:19:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I said the same thing after that last basketball match.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.91,0:19:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Although someone fell asleep and didn't hear me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.62,0:19:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I'm just... no good without you, Koizumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.42,0:19:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So... that wasn't a dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.77,0:19:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Koizumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.79,0:20:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you pull a better face than that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.23,0:20:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.97,0:20:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.94,0:20:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have a fever again?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.64,0:20:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.44,0:20:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... Not like that... Not like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.18,0:20:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.21,0:21:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.48,0:21:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I still dreaming?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.46,0:21:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't a dream, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.56,0:23:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,My first date with Otani!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.06,0:23:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You're late!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.96,0:23:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you buy me juice as penance?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.49,0:23:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! I forgot my purse...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.69,0:23:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.76,0:23:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Lovely Complex ~ Love Com.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.53,0:23:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Next: Sudden Downturn!! The First Date is the Beginning of Misfortune!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.30,0:23:20.00,Preview Title,,0,0,0,,Sudden Downturn!! The First Date is the Beginning of Misfortune!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.80,0:23:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Be sure to watch!
